# -*- mode: snippet -*-
# name: Checklist: New Product/Project
# key: checklist_product
# --
- [ ] How will this provide value?
- [ ] What business problem will this solve?
- [ ] Is this the best solution possible?
- [ ] What other solutions were considered?
- [ ] RACI: Who's Responsible, Accountible, Consulted and Informed?
- [ ] ICE: Impact x Confidence x Ease
  - Impact: how will this improve the key metric(s)
  - Ease: how easy is this to implement?
  - Confidence: how sure are we about the Impact and Ease?